00:15:28.110 --> 00:15:29.640
die in the Holocaust, which was a miracle.

00:15:29.640 --> 00:15:33.760
But she still had hate, hatred towards the
German people.

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:36.560
And when she moved to America she got married,
had children.

