00:16:05.060 --> 00:16:07.340
Sid: I can't wait for that. Thank you, Janie.

00:16:07.340 --> 00:16:12.920
Now Margy, here you are in the car with this
psychopath who's murdered 30 women that looked

00:16:12.920 --> 00:16:15.430
just you, murdered and raped.

00:16:15.430 --> 00:16:20.810
And all of a sudden he's taking direction
from you because God supernaturally– He realized

00:16:20.810 --> 00:16:23.040
it's God speaking through you.

00:16:23.040 --> 00:16:29.700
And he even had the trust to let you call
your husband?

00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:30.440
Margy: Yeah.

00:16:30.440 --> 00:16:31.500
He told me to call my husband.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:35.940
So I called home and all of a sudden–
Sid: Why did he tell you to call your husband?

00:16:35.950 --> 00:16:40.050
Margy: Well you know, he said, all day he
kept saying, "I don't know if I'm going to

00:16:40.050 --> 00:16:41.720
be able to let you go or not."

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:44.140
And you know, he just changed his mind.

00:16:44.140 --> 00:16:45.430
He said, "Call your husband."

00:16:45.430 --> 00:16:51.860
So I called my husband and when my husband
answered the phone, all of a sudden, the calm

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:54.230
that I had all day went out the window.

00:16:54.230 --> 00:16:55.530
I started shaking.

00:16:55.530 --> 00:16:56.530
Sid: I'm sure.

00:16:56.530 --> 00:17:00.460
Margy: When I heard his voice I started thinking,
am I going to see my family again and things

00:17:00.460 --> 00:17:01.500
like that.

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:06.880
And anyway, when I got off the phone, Stephen
was standing there with the gun on me, and

00:17:06.890 --> 00:17:09.509
he said, "You're really upset."

00:17:09.509 --> 00:17:15.080
And I put my hands on him and I said, "In
Jesus' name, I take authority in Jesus' name

00:17:15.080 --> 00:17:18.380
over the spirit of fear and command it to
leave me."

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:21.949
And it left immediately, and that peace came
back on me.

00:17:21.949 --> 00:17:25.010
And I said–
Sid: Why didn't you tell your husband what

00:17:25.010 --> 00:17:26.010
was going on?

00:17:26.010 --> 00:17:27.189
He wouldn't have known.

00:17:27.189 --> 00:17:28.519
Margy: Because Stephen was standing right
there.

00:17:28.519 --> 00:17:29.519
Sid: Oh I see.

00:17:29.519 --> 00:17:32.029
Margy: Yeah, he was standing right there with
a gun on me when I was on the phone.

00:17:32.029 --> 00:17:33.029
Sid: Okay.

00:17:33.029 --> 00:17:34.029
Margy: So I couldn't tell him.

00:17:34.029 --> 00:17:37.100
And he knew something was wrong, and he kept
saying, what's the matter.

00:17:37.100 --> 00:17:38.950
I said, "I'll be home later.

00:17:38.950 --> 00:17:39.950
I'm out shopping."

00:17:39.950 --> 00:17:40.970
It was Christmas time.

00:17:40.970 --> 00:17:44.740
So you know, he just let it go at that.

00:17:44.740 --> 00:17:47.909
And so after I got off the phone I was shaken
up.

00:17:47.909 --> 00:17:51.490
But God's peace came back on me right after
I prayed.

00:17:51.490 --> 00:17:57.070
And we got back in the car and started going
up to Kerrville where I had seen God showed

00:17:57.070 --> 00:17:58.330
us to go.

00:17:58.330 --> 00:18:04.740
And so on the over out there, Stephen started
telling me that he had this son.

00:18:04.740 --> 00:18:07.150
And he said, "I haven't told you this, but
I have a son."

00:18:07.150 --> 00:18:10.240
And I said, "Well I want to ask you a question.

00:18:10.240 --> 00:18:13.950
If this son had committed the same crimes
that you've committed, I don't know what they

00:18:13.950 --> 00:18:20.570
are, if he had done exactly what you did and
had done, would you be willing to die for

00:18:20.570 --> 00:18:27.520
him and let's just say there is hell, would
you be willing to go hell and pay for all

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:31.870
of these crimes, that God would say, you do
this, you're going to pay for every crime

00:18:31.870 --> 00:18:33.070
that your son has committed.

00:18:33.070 --> 00:18:36.740
Would you be willing to die and go to hell
for him?

00:18:36.740 --> 00:18:43.340
And I want to know if you could still love
your son if he had done those kind of crimes?

00:18:43.340 --> 00:18:45.020
Would you forgive him?"

00:18:45.020 --> 00:18:46.680
Sid: That's a very penetrating question.

00:18:46.690 --> 00:18:47.809
Margy: So it was.

00:18:47.809 --> 00:18:49.899
He said, "Well that's a hard question, lady."

00:18:49.899 --> 00:18:51.470
And I said, "You need to answer it.

00:18:51.470 --> 00:18:52.500
I want you to answer me."

00:18:52.500 --> 00:18:55.601
And he said, "Well you know what–"
Sid: You're saying to a man, a psychopath

00:18:55.601 --> 00:18:58.500
with a gun that you need to answer it.

00:18:58.500 --> 00:19:03.040
Lady, you got chutzpah.

00:19:03.040 --> 00:19:08.620
Margy: So he said, "You know what, I would
die for my son.

00:19:08.620 --> 00:19:13.159
I would die for him and I would forgive him."

00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:17.880
And I said, "Well you know, that's exactly
what Jesus Christ did for you."

00:19:17.880 --> 00:19:25.379
And he just looked at me and he said, "You've
been preaching to me all day and I finally

00:19:25.380 --> 00:19:27.860
understand what you're trying to say."

00:19:27.860 --> 00:19:32.480
And then we just kind of drove on in silence
for a while, and all of a sudden he pulled

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:37.880
my car over to the side of the road, and he
was looking all around my car.

00:19:37.880 --> 00:19:44.340
He looked in back of him and all over the
place, and I didn't know what he was doing.

00:19:44.340 --> 00:19:45.429
Sid: What was he looking for?

00:19:45.429 --> 00:19:50.269
Margy: Well he stopped my car on the side
of the road after looking all over the place,

00:19:50.269 --> 00:19:56.039
and then his hands went up in the air like
this, and he said, "Jesus, I'm sorry for everything

00:19:56.039 --> 00:19:57.039
I've ever done.

00:19:57.039 --> 00:19:58.039
Please forgive me.

00:19:58.040 --> 00:19:59.300
I want to go to Heaven."

00:19:59.300 --> 00:20:04.720
And I just sat there staring at him because
I had not said to do that.

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:09.600
But what had happened was, he told me later,
he said, "Remember when I was looking around

00:20:09.600 --> 00:20:10.120
the car?"

00:20:10.120 --> 00:20:10.840
And I said, yes.

00:20:10.840 --> 00:20:17.620
He said, "I heard an audible voice," and he
said, "it came from up here and it said to

00:20:17.629 --> 00:20:22.299
me, "This is the last time I'm going to call
you, Stephen.'"

00:20:22.299 --> 00:20:28.030
So he said, "When I heard that voice," now
I didn't hear it, but he heard it.

00:20:28.030 --> 00:20:29.789
And he said, "It was very loud."

00:20:29.789 --> 00:20:32.279
He said, "I knew it was Jesus."

00:20:32.279 --> 00:20:37.760
And he said, "I knew all day everything that
had gone on," you know, he said, "I could

00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:45.139
just see the peace that you had and everything,
I realized that this was not a joke.

00:20:45.139 --> 00:20:50.389
Everything you said was true and there really
was a Jesus, there is a Jesus and this was

00:20:50.389 --> 00:20:52.580
not something you made up."

00:20:52.580 --> 00:20:57.509
He said, "I had thought it was just, you know,
you had this strong faith, but I knew it was

00:20:57.509 --> 00:20:58.540
something real."

00:20:58.540 --> 00:21:02.740
Sid: So look, he's one of the ten most wanted
men in America.

00:21:02.740 --> 00:21:04.840
There's helicopters going all over.

00:21:04.840 --> 00:21:06.420
Everyone is looking for him.

00:21:06.429 --> 00:21:09.129
They're furious to find him.

00:21:09.129 --> 00:21:11.800
What did he do next now that he believes in
Jesus?

00:21:11.800 --> 00:21:17.110
Margy: Well I mean, at that point in the car,
you know, when he put his hands up after hearing

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:20.070
this voice, he started crying.

00:21:20.070 --> 00:21:22.269
And he said, "It's gone.

00:21:22.269 --> 00:21:23.269
It's gone."

00:21:23.269 --> 00:21:24.289
And I said, "What's gone?"

00:21:24.289 --> 00:21:29.570
And he said, "Lady, something just came in
me and all the hatred is gone out of me."

00:21:29.570 --> 00:21:35.399
He said, "I've been hating and hating, and
I hated myself, and hated everybody else,

00:21:35.399 --> 00:21:37.450
and I feel like I've been cleaned.

00:21:37.450 --> 00:21:38.651
I'm clean now."

00:21:38.651 --> 00:21:43.149
And I said, "Well you have, what the Bible
says, you have been born again."

00:21:43.149 --> 00:21:45.840
He said, "What in the world is that?"

00:21:45.840 --> 00:21:51.059
And I said, "When you got born the first time
you have an earthly mother and father, and

00:21:51.059 --> 00:21:54.029
you have their blood in you.

00:21:54.029 --> 00:21:55.610
You are their seed.

00:21:55.610 --> 00:22:01.919
Well when you ask Jesus to come into your
life he puts his seed into you, which is eternal

00:22:01.919 --> 00:22:07.460
life, and he becomes, God becomes your father
and Jesus' blood comes into you.

00:22:07.460 --> 00:22:13.140
You have supernatural DNA and he washes your
sins away supernaturally."

00:22:13.140 --> 00:22:14.840
I said, "It's supernatural."

00:22:14.840 --> 00:22:19.040
And he said, "I don't deserve this."

00:22:19.040 --> 00:22:22.960
He said, "I don't deserve it, but I feel like
I'm clean, lady."

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:25.070
And he was overwhelmed with this feeling.

00:22:25.070 --> 00:22:28.889
And so then we drove on up to Kerrville.

00:22:28.889 --> 00:22:33.691
And when we got there, I went into the bus
station, and I said, "Is there a bus going

00:22:33.691 --> 00:22:35.320
to Austin any time soon?"

00:22:35.320 --> 00:22:38.100
And he said, "In 30 minutes there's a bus
going."

00:22:38.100 --> 00:22:44.300
So he, Stephen and I sat there waiting for
this bus, and when I went back to the car,

00:22:44.300 --> 00:22:46.700
he said, "Don't tell me, there's a bus going
to Fort Worth."

00:22:46.700 --> 00:22:50.280
And I said, "Yeah, the next bus coming in
is going to Fort Worth."

00:22:50.280 --> 00:22:55.200
So they eventually caught him and he was executed.

00:22:55.200 --> 00:23:00.640
But there is a big prison ministry now as
a result of his life.

00:23:00.640 --> 00:23:03.060
Sid: What did he say to the police officer
that arrested him?

00:23:03.060 --> 00:23:10.640
Margy: Well he said, "If I had seen you earlier
this morning there would have been a shoot-out

00:23:10.640 --> 00:23:15.240
and I would have killed myself, but I met
this lady today and she changed my life, and

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:17.700
I'll never be the same again."

00:23:17.700 --> 00:23:21.540
Sid: Looking back in retrospect, how could
you have done that, Margy?

00:23:21.549 --> 00:23:22.549
Margy: I couldn't have done it.

00:23:22.549 --> 00:23:23.789
Sid: How could you have gone through this?

00:23:23.789 --> 00:23:25.780
Margy: I couldn't have done it without Jesus.

00:23:25.780 --> 00:23:26.780
It wouldn't be possible.

00:23:26.780 --> 00:23:27.780
Sid: I mean, you're just a mom.

00:23:27.780 --> 00:23:30.040
Margy: I know, I am.

00:23:30.040 --> 00:23:33.360
Well I mean, I couldn't do it without Jesus.

00:23:33.360 --> 00:23:38.480
But that morning I said, I will never forget
this, that morning I said, "God, I'll do anything

00:23:38.480 --> 00:23:40.180
you want me to do for you."

00:23:40.180 --> 00:23:45.239
Don't ever say that if you don't mean it because
God had literally used me.

00:23:45.239 --> 00:23:46.239
Sid: Had you not done that?

00:23:46.239 --> 00:23:47.549
Margy: Had I not done that I'd be dead.

00:23:47.549 --> 00:23:48.200
Sid: You'd be dead.

00:23:48.200 --> 00:23:48.740
Margy: I'd be dead.

00:23:48.740 --> 00:23:50.240
Sid: Did you hear that?

00:23:50.240 --> 00:23:56.919
Remember the voice that this man heard, "This
is your last chance."

00:23:56.919 --> 00:24:02.669
I believe that some of you that are watching
me right now, God has been calling you for

00:24:02.669 --> 00:24:10.180
a long time and this is your last, last chance.

00:24:10.180 --> 00:24:14.000
Pray this prayer with me and mean it to the
best of your ability.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:18.460
I don't care what you have done, God loves
you.

00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:22.560
His love is pouring right through this television
set right now.

00:24:22.560 --> 00:24:25.960
There is something happening to you and that's
God's spirit.

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:33.360
Repeat this prayer: Dear God, out loud, Dear
God, I'm a sinner.

00:24:33.360 --> 00:24:37.860
Against you and you alone have I sinned.

00:24:37.860 --> 00:24:49.160
I believe that Jesus died for my sins and
because of his blood I am clean.

00:24:49.160 --> 00:24:56.520
And now that I am clean, I make Jesus my
Messiah and Lord.

00:24:56.520 --> 00:25:02.820
Lord Jesus, come inside of me, take over my
life.

00:25:02.820 --> 00:25:08.210
I need to know my Father God.

00:25:08.210 --> 00:25:11.619
I need to know the goodness of God.

00:25:11.620 --> 00:25:20.260
My earthly father made mistakes, but O God,
your love is being poured into me right now.

00:25:20.260 --> 00:25:21.360
Fill me.

00:25:21.360 --> 00:25:28.900
Say this out loud, fill me in Jesus' name
with your Holy Spirit.

00:25:28.900 --> 00:25:31.680
You see, because of Jesus, you've been made
whole.

00:25:31.690 --> 00:25:34.580
God says, "I remember your sins no more."

00:25:34.580 --> 00:25:37.520
Fill them right now, O God.

00:25:37.520 --> 00:25:47.040
Let them experience the love of the Father,
the love, the clean, undefiled love of the

00:25:47.040 --> 00:25:48.400
Father.

00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:56.360
Let them experience your peace and let nothing
separate them from your love.

00:25:56.360 --> 00:26:01.180
Let nothing ever separate them again.

00:26:01.180 --> 00:26:08.820
I urge you to get a Bible, start reading it
and start telling God how much you love him

00:26:08.820 --> 00:26:11.940
because you are special.

00:26:11.940 --> 00:26:15.660
God really, really loves you.

00:26:15.660 --> 00:26:17.260
He really does.

00:26:17.260 --> 00:26:19.380
He sent me here to tell you.

00:26:19.380 --> 00:26:21.040
That's why I'm here.

00:26:21.040 --> 00:26:22.260
He loves you.

00:26:22.360 --> 00:26:24.620
He loves you. He does.

